\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs26 1. Executive Summary\b0\fs22\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1
VouRifar is a Brazilian SaaS platform that enables organizers to create and manage online raffles (\'93rifas\'94) with automated PIX payment processing. The Google Ads API integration is an \b internal marketing automation tool\b0  used exclusively by VouRifar platform administrators to create, manage, and monitor Google Search campaigns that drive user acquisition for the VouRifar platform.\par
\par
This tool is \b not offered to third parties\b0  and is not a public-facing product. End users (raffle organizers and buyers) never interact with the Google Ads API. Only authorized VouRifar staff access campaign management features through a secured super-admin interface and CLI scripts.\par
\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs26 2. Business Model and Purpose of API Usage\b0\fs22\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b 2.1 Business model\b0\par
VouRifar operates as a multi-tenant SaaS platform. Organizers register for free, create raffle campaigns, and receive payments via PIX (through Mercado Pago Direct or platform-managed Woovi). The platform earns a commission (5\'967%) on each sale. Revenue depends on acquiring new organizers to the platform.\par
\par
\b 2.2 Why we use the Google Ads API\b0\par
We use the Google Ads API to programmatically:\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa120 Create and manage Search campaigns promoting VouRifar to potential raffle organizers in Brazil.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Create ad groups, keywords, and responsive search ads with consistent messaging and landing page URLs.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Pause, enable, or adjust budgets and bids based on performance without manual changes in the Google Ads web UI.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Retrieve campaign performance metrics (impressions, clicks, conversions, cost) for internal reporting dashboards.\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\par

\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs26 3. Tool Overview\b0\fs22\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b 3.1 Tool name\b0\par
VouRifar Google Ads Campaign Manager (internal component of the VouRifar platform)\par
\par
\b 3.2 Users\b0\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa120\b Internal only:\b0  VouRifar platform administrators (1\'963 authorized staff accounts).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\b External users:\b0  None. Organizers and buyers on vourifar.com.br do not access Google Ads functionality.\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\par
\b 3.3 Deployment\b0\par
The tool runs on VouRifar\'92s production VPS (Node.js/Express application) and local development environments. Google Ads credentials are stored as server-side environment variables and are never exposed to browsers or end users.\par
\par

