\par
\b 4.2 Technology stack\b0\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa120 Runtime: Node.js 22+, Express.js\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Authentication to Google: OAuth 2.0 (offline access, refresh token stored in environment variables)\par
