\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b\fs26 12. Summary\b0\fs22\par
\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1
VouRifar requests Basic Access to the Google Ads API to manage its own Search advertising campaigns for platform user acquisition. The integration is internal, low-volume, server-side, and uses standard OAuth 2.0 authentication. We will use Search campaign management and reporting capabilities only, with estimated usage far below Basic Access daily limits.\par
\par
